Bachelor of Arts

Bachelor of Arts is a 3 years full time degree program affiliated to University of Mumbai. It gives students a broad foundation in the humanities, social sciences, and other liberal arts. A BA degree opens up many career opportunities including teaching, media, communication, arts, culture, business, public sector, and the creative industries. It has strong career prospects and helps students specialize in various fields.

{/* First Year */}

First Year B.A (F.Y.B.A)

Semester I

  • History (Ancient India)
  • Economics (Microeconomics-I)
  • Geography
  • Basics of Agriculture-I
  • Introduction to Indian Archeology
  • Indian Constitution
  • Communication skills in English
  • Indian Knowledge System

Semester II
